title: Coronavirus Doctor - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 4/17/20

description:
George Noory takes an open lines call from an emergency room doctor who gives a first hand account of how his hospital is handling increased cases of the coronavirus, and explains that the disease is much more serious than skeptics believe.
